----------------------------------------------------------------------
OPTIONAL dependency — the `[ner]` extra (Hebrew named-entity recognition)
----------------------------------------------------------------------

Enabling the `[ner]` extra pulls:
  - Hugging Face Transformers (Apache-2.0)
  - PyTorch (BSD-3-Clause)

and uses the following model, which carries an ATTRIBUTION requirement:

  dicta-il/dictabert-ner — Hebrew Named-Entity Recognition model by DICTA.
    Authors:  Shaltiel Shmidman, Avi Shmidman, Moshe Koppel (DICTA / Bar-Ilan University)
    Model:    https://huggingface.co/dicta-il/dictabert-ner
    Project:  https://dicta.org.il/dicta-bert
    License:  Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)
              https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/
              "This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
               International License."

    If you enable the [ner] extra you must retain this attribution. The model is
    used as-is (not modified) and is downloaded at runtime, not redistributed here.

    Citation:
      @misc{shmidman2023dictabert,
            title={DictaBERT: A State-of-the-Art BERT Suite for Modern Hebrew},
            author={Shaltiel Shmidman and Avi Shmidman and Moshe Koppel},
            year={2023},
            eprint={2308.16687},
            archivePrefix={arXiv},
            primaryClass={cs.CL}
      }
